==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Explication
<hw>Ex`pli*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>explicatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>explication</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act of opening, unfolding, or explaining; explanation;
exposition; interpretation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>explication</qex> of our Savior's parables.</q>
<rj><qau>Atterbury.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The sense given by an expositor.</def> <rj><au>Bp.
Burnet.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Explicative</ent>⟦br⟧
